Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101956,103333}"Cherry blossom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105126,107795}We learned it in\NEnglish class, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:49.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107795,109547}It's the English words for "Sakura".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110632,112383}Oh, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:56.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112383,116763}There's a painting called\N"Cherry Blossom" at the Central Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116763,118306}Oh, I know about that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:06.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119307,126439}Isn't that the masterpiece so admired\Nfor it's life-like withering petals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126439,129442}I'd like to see it once myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130443,132820}You're going to steal the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132820,134781}Rather, I'd like you to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134781,136240}Get it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:22.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137784,142038}An old man came to me\Nfor help yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:29.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143873,149754}He says that the owner\Nof the museum deceived him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149754,151422}Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:37.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152090,157428}The old man thought he signed a contract\Nto loan "Cherry Blossom" to the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:41.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157428,161391}Later he found out they had\Nswitched the contract
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161391,164060}to one that transferred\Nownership of the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167230,169399}What is that?! How mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:55.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170066,175571}The modern art exhibition\Nhas just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175571,176989}So during the…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176989,178366}I get the idea, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178825,181786}Just leave the rest to St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.79,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:184622,187792}A Formidable Enemy!\NNew Student, Rina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194799,196092}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196092,197635}I still can't beat this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197635,198636}Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:21.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198636,201723}And I've used up\Nthis month's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202265,204016}Hey, where's Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204016,205351}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205768,207854}He's been like that the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215319,216154}Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216154,218990}Hey, I think you should retreat a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218990,220074}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:46.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222827,226122}That's from you butting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226122,227331}No, dodge those!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227331,228541}And those, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:49.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228541,229667}Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229667,231961}Now, punch!\NNo, dodge again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231961,233921}What are you doing?!\NDon't kick yet! Jump! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233921,235548}Go now! Now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235548,236799}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238718,240720}Quit your yakking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242805,245266}You're so frustrating.\NHere, let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246350,248019}What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252565,253858}You…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254150,255985}Bad form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255985,257570}Whose fault is that, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258237,259989}Just who the heck are you anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259989,261866}Butting into other people's business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:26.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262492,266746}Your interference ruined my game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267789,269540}Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269540,271542}Hold on, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272043,273044}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:39.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274003,279008}"I'm going to the Central Museum\Ntomorrow night to get Cherry Blossom".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:40.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280009,280760}This is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283054,285389}It's a warning from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286599,287892}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:48.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287892,288643}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288643,289936}Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:55.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289936,295233}You're living in this town and you don't\Nknow St. Tail? What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295942,299195}How rude! I just moved here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300613,301656}Hey, she's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302824,304784}She's taller than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305493,307370}I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307370,309664}– I have to think up a strategy!\N– Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310623,311958}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313000,316295}St. Tail, I'll get you\Nfor sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316295,318047}Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318047,319006}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:22.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319006,322677}Sheesh, I 'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323761,326472}– I said hold on!\N– You 're annoying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331060,332436}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342780,344949}You 're not very fit, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344949,346242}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346242,349412}Hey, tell me about St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350121,351330}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352748,355251}Hey, what are you doing?!\NCut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355251,357962}So, you gonna tell me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:58.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357962,358963}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360923,362717}Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362717,365011}Okay, I'll tell you!\NLet go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365970,368973}Ooh, that hurt.\NI thought I was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:10.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368973,370933}I'm sorry, did that really hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370933,372143}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372143,373102}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373561,376480}St. Tail is a girl thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376480,378858}Oh, a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379150,381444}That means she's a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381444,382486}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:26.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382486,386908}Her true identity is unknown. But she's\Nso sly, that the police can't catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386908,389327}The police can't catch her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393164,394457}I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394457,396792}Where's the Central Museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:41.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397919,401714}At Third Ave and Bay Street, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401714,403507}OK, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403507,405301}Sorry if I was a bit rough on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405843,408763}I'm Rina Takamiya.\NI'm 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408763,409764}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411474,413309}What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414268,416729}Time to eat, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416729,417980}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418564,420441}Wow, it looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420441,421192}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423569,425029}Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425029,426197}Now call Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426405,427406}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433996,435414}You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435414,436958}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437500,438793}What am I gonna do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439543,441253}What are you doing, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441253,442713}Hmm? This.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443255,445132}Those are Tarot cards, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445132,446008}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:29.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446008,449512}I'm wondering if I can use tarot card\Nfortune telling to do some new magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449512,453724}That sounds like fun!\NWill you try it on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453724,455226}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471867,473369}What's wrong, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475121,477081}Is anything wrong with that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480001,482586}Mama, don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483170,484755}Really, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484755,486841}You should keep your mind\Non the task at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487508,489051}It's time for dinner, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489802,490886}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492596,494265}What's so funny, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494265,495057}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495057,497685}It's just that you and Meimi\Ndo the things the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497685,498728}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499103,502606}I'm a little worried\Nabout Meimi, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502606,504108}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:28.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504108,508487}According to the cards,\Nshe's in for a bit of an ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508904,510197}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:36.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511198,516162}She'll be all right, because like me,\Nher best feature is her cheerfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516162,517288}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:41.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517288,521000}And besides, my bad fortune telling\Nis probably wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521000,524462}Well, well, what's\Nfor dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524462,527548}Today it's your favorite, beef stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527548,528966}That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528966,531802}Papa, Mama, I'm gonna start eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531802,533012}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536599,537892}Oh, I'm full.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543606,545149}Come on, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:10.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546776,550738}I can't today, I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551739,552615}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558454,559663}OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560456,563918}Oh, I forgot to ask Papa\Nabout the tarot cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563918,565169}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565169,566796}I'll just give it my all today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:36.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573219,576847}Forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581769,582853}One…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585356,586524}Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588567,589819}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:09.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605960,609797}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611882,613801}It's gonna be great today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613801,616804}Meimi, be careful tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:17.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617054,617805}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617805,620474}I feel strangely uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:24.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620474,624270}You mean Asuka Jr.?\NHe's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:30.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624520,630901}Not Asuka Jr., something else.\NSomething else is going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632403,634738}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:39.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635239,639785}So long as the blessings of God are with us,\Nthere's nothing St. Tail can't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639785,641620}Well, I better go.
Comment: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:44.66,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:644665,644665}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:50.67,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:650671,650671}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:55.67,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:655676,655676}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664435,665144}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667021,668647}Everyone is in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669273,670816}All right, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671400,674653}If you see someone suspicious,\Ndon't let him get away, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674653,675529}We found this one loitering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675529,676614}Whaa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676614,677364}Come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677364,679617}All right, I'm coming,\Nyou don't have to pull me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680201,681368}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:22.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681994,682828}Hey, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684121,685289}It's you…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686081,688542}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:32.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688542,692671}You're in charge of security?\NWow, you're only in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692880,695799}I'm in Junior High and\NI'm the same age as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695799,696759}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:41.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697092,701222}She insists that she's authorized personnel\Nand refuses to move from the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:44.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701722,704350}Asuka Jr., this one is a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:47.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704350,707186}Maybe she's St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:54.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709438,714652}Take your filthy hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716153,719657}I'm going to stand\Nguard over here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719657,720616}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:06.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722910,726538}I was appointed by the Mayor\Nto investigate St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726538,728832}You can't go around doing whatever\Nyou want without my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729416,730834}The Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731627,732795}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733170,736090}The Mayor happens to be my Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736882,738592}Which makes you\Nthe Mayor's niece?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:23.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738592,743639}Yes! Besides, we've got a lot\Nof our paintings here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743639,745266}We can't have a thief breaking in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745432,746558}But… but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746934,749895}Well, you go ahead and\Ndo what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750938,752564}Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754275,756026}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756193,758529}Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774878,776547}"Cherry Blossom"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777256,779675}It's splendid, just as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:07.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784847,787683}Hey, cut it out!\NThat's so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788600,789977}You know, it's all because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791061,792146}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792521,795232}It's St. Tail.\NDon't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795232,796525}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796525,798610}Don't panic! Switch on\Nthe emergency lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:25.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801071,805034}All right! Everyone, check\Nup on your assigned posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805034,805868}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805868,808037}Cherry Blossom is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808037,809038}It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811999,813167}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817338,819131}This is a cherry blossom petal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819131,820466}There are more trailing off that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822760,826680}If we follow the trail,\Nwe' ll run into the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827139,828932}Hold it!\NDon't go acting on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829600,832019}Why don't you stay here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:57.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832019,837775}I have confidence in my legs and my\Nstrength, so I'll go nab the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838067,839276}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:04.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841111,844573}Oh shoot! That's her way of\Nthrowing us into confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:17.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852790,857878}Hey, maybe that girl has\Nalready caught St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857878,860672}Could be. That would really\Nmake us look like fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:24.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860672,864468}All right! We'll follow the\Ncherry blossom petals! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864468,865511}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:29.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865511,869014}{\i1}Darn it, I'm the one who's\Ngoing to capture St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873143,875979}Hmm… pretty good…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876146,878482}But not clever enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880442,882903}I wonder who that girl is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:49.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884613,889576}Here I have with me a piece of cloth.\NNothing up my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:55.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892871,895541}The masterpiece, Cherry Blossom,\Nthat disappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895541,896834}Appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:05.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904550,905717}Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:10.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907594,910722}As a matter of fact,\NI didn't steal it, yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911849,914226}I'm not letting you\Nget away, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915727,917062}So, that's the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923902,927614}Hold it! Hold it!\NHold it! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927614,930451}I'm the one who's capturing St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:34.45,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:928949,934455}Please keep the supply closet clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935664,938083}Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938083,940419}And just why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:44.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940711,944381}I couldn't help it.\NThe petals led me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944381,947009}This is St. Tail's usual\Nway of confusing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:50.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947009,950179}Which means you fell for\Nthe same trick every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952264,954892}There are more petals.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955684,957227}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960481,962733}Hey! Isn't this her usual trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962733,963525}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963525,966153}You are just worried about\Nyour paintings, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966153,967821}That's all you're worried about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967821,969156}What? You actually\Nbelieved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969156,970199}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970199,972826}What I told you were\Nobviously all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972826,974328}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980250,982753}They say that lying makes a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:28.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983420,988717}{\an8}Even a thief possesses an ounce of logic!\NThis is absurd! Don't you forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985172,988717}In other words, you're pretty bad\Nat avoiding and dodging things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992804,995516}What's this?\NWe're outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995516,996683}There's something strange going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997351,1000646}Although it's not the right season,\Nthe cherry blossom is in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001146,1002231}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002648,1004399}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004775,1007402}Up there, on top of that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010572,1012366}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012908,1015118}St. Tail? That's her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:59.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015410,1019081}Good work. I'm taking\NCherry Blossom with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019414,1020499}Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020499,1021750}Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:08.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022292,1028757}When I grow up, I'll become a police\Nofficer. And I'll arrest St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029258,1032594}No way! If anyone arrests St. Tail,\Nit'll be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032594,1035013}It really doesn't matter\Nwho arrests her, does it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:15.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035013,1035973}Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:16.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035973,1036890}Nyaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037224,1040143}I know it's not the right season,\Nbut I'll give you two a free show
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040143,1041937}of falling cherry blossom petals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045190,1047818}It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060581,1061373}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078974,1080225}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080892,1082561}Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082561,1084855}Hey! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085772,1086773}What? Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089443,1090736}She's outwitted me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:17.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093488,1097701}Humph! She may be a thief,\Nbut she's just a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098285,1101413}If only you didn't get in my way,\NI would have captured her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103123,1105667}You really are so…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136114,1137449}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149795,1151672}Good morning, Meimi.\NYou're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151963,1154341}Oh, good morning, Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:19.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155384,1159179}Seira… nothing happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169898,1171817}Miss Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172317,1174736}Oh, good morning, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174736,1177781}Good morning, Miss Haneoka.\NI'd like you to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:41.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177781,1181743}This is a new student who will be in\Nyour class. Please take her with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181743,1183578}Sure, I'd be glad to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183578,1184579}Miss Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.58,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1184579,1186581}ST. TAIL EXPOSES MUSEUM SWINDLE\NOwner Arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:50.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189918,1190794}{\i1}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:55.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191837,1195424}This is Rina Takamiya, a new\Nstudent who has just arrived today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195424,1196341}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197968,1199344}{\i1}She's… yesterday's…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:01.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200053,1201096}{\i1}Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201430,1203265}{\i1}I'll become a police officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:12.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208854,1212107}Please take care of her,\NMiss Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212107,1213483}Uh… yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:20.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216278,1220949}You keep staring at me.\NIs there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:25.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220949,1225328}No. I'm Meimi Haneoka,\Nglad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:28.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225328,1228123}If you ever need anything,\Njust ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228123,1230542}Okay. I do have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231042,1234045}There's this boy I'd like\Nto meet, named Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234045,1235505}Is he at this school?
